---
import Site from '../layouts/Site.astro';
import { SITE } from '../data/site';
const updated = 'July 2026';
---
<Site title="Terms of Use & Disclaimer" description="Terms of use and disclaimer for the Mangalam Coalfield Private Limited website, including the public regulations library.">
  <section class="relative bg-background px-6 pb-24 pt-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <span class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-primary">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="mt-3 font-[var(--font-display)] text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground md:text-5xl">Terms of Use &amp; Disclaimer</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground">Last updated: {updated}</p>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-8 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-[var(--font-display)] text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">1. About this website</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">This website is operated by {SITE.legalName} ("Mangalam", "we", "us"). By accessing or using it you agree to these Terms of Use and the <a href="/privacy" class="text-primary underline">Privacy Notice</a>. If you do not agree, please do not use the site.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-[var(--font-display)] text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">2. Informational purpose &amp; no warranty</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">The content on this site — including operational information, explainers and the regulations library — is provided for general information only. While we make reasonable efforts to keep it accurate and current, we make no warranty, express or implied, as to its accuracy, completeness or fitness for any purpose, and we accept no liability for any loss arising from reliance on it.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-[var(--font-display)] text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">3. Regulations &amp; official sources</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">Statutes, rules, regulations, notifications and DGMS circulars reproduced or linked here are Government of India public-domain documents, provided as a convenience for public reference. They are <strong class="text-foreground/80">not</strong> official copies. Always verify the current, in-force text against the official publication (e.g. DGMS, the Ministry of Coal, the Ministry of Labour &amp; Employment, or the Gazette of India) before relying on it. Nothing here is legal, safety, financial or professional advice.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-[var(--font-display)] text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">4. No commitments</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">Information on this site, including any material generated by the "Ask Mangalam" assistant, does not constitute an offer, quotation, hiring commitment, or contractual promise on behalf of Mangalam. Recruitment, commercial and other decisions are made only through our formal processes and written communications.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-[var(--font-display)] text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">5. Intellectual property</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">The Mangalam name, logo, site design and original content are the property of {SITE.legalName}. Government documents remain in the public domain. You may view and download material for lawful personal or professional reference; you may not misrepresent its source.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-[var(--font-display)] text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">6. External links</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">We link to third-party and government websites for convenience. We are not responsible for the content, availability or practices of those sites.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-[var(--font-display)] text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">7. Data protection</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">Personal data you submit (enquiries, job applications) is handled in line with the Digital Personal Data Protection Act, 2023, as described in our <a href="/privacy" class="text-primary underline">Privacy Notice</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-[var(--font-display)] text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">8. Governing law</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">These terms are governed by the laws of India, and the courts at the company's registered jurisdiction shall have exclusive jurisdiction.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-[var(--font-display)] text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">9. Contact</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">Questions about these terms? Email <a href={`mailto:${SITE.hrEmail}`} class="text-primary underline">{SITE.hrEmail}</a> or call <a href={`tel:${SITE.phoneHref}`} class="text-primary underline">{SITE.phone}</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Site>
